Package: ClussCluster
Type: Package
Title: Simultaneous Detection of Clusters and Cluster-Specific Genes in High-throughput Transcriptome Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ge Jiang, Jun Li
Maintainer: Ge Jiang <gjiang2@nd.edu>
Description: This package implements a new method ClussCluster to simultaneously perform clustering analysis and signature gene selection on high-dimensional transcriptome data sets. To do so, ClussCluster incorporates a Lasso-type regularization penalty term to the objective function of K-means so that cell-type-specific signature genes can be identified while clustering the cells.
Depends: R (>= 2.10.0)
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports: stats, utils,grid, VennDiagram, scales, reshape2, ggplot2
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
